reviewText:
This is the most fabricated film ever. Trying to make a little $?
At least LEARN with Michael Moore and use the TRUTH to do it.

This documentary illustrates how the clinton's manipulate,at the expense of unsuspecting friends all for the gain of power. This is nothing we don't know,However most allegations never see the light because of media lapdogs,who somehow continue to have disdain for any story or comment that lends itself to potential corruption at the hands of Bill or Hillary, And therefore is convieniently and quietly covered up. Unfortunately many years from now we will learn how corrupt they were when the truth is finally uncovered.

What Bill and Hillary and their attack dogs (i.e. Clintonistas) did to Peter Paul is nothing short of a crime.  This documentary which features home video of Bill and Hillary proves that this woman should not be President; let alone a Senator.  Ten stars of Mr. Paul having the guts to tell his story.
